import React, { Fragment, Component } from 'react'
import PropTypes from 'prop-types'
import ColorScheme from '../../libs/ColorScheme'
import Modal from 'react-bootstrap/Modal'

class ColorSchemeModal extends Component {

    render () {
        return (
            <Modal show={this.props.shouldShow} onHide={this.props.cancelSelected}>
                <Modal.Header closeButton>
                <Modal.Title>Modal heading</Modal.Title>
                </Modal.Header>
                <Modal.Body>Woohoo, you're reading this text in a modal!</Modal.Body>
                <Modal.Footer>
                <button variant="secondary" onClick={this.props.cancelSelected}>
                    Close
                </button>
                </Modal.Footer>
            </Modal>
        )
    }
}

ColorSchemeModal.propTypes = {
    shouldShow: PropTypes.bool.isRequired,
    colorSchemeSelected: PropTypes.func.isRequired,
    cancelSelected: PropTypes.func.isRequired
}

export default ColorSchemeModal
